OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FKeir Starmer is under sustained
OL,7,Fpressure amid reports he could stand
OL,8,Fdown next week as a leadership threat
OL,9,Ffrom Andy Burnham looms.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister has repeatedly
OL,12,Fvowed not to walk away from his post,
OL,13,Feven as public talk of a leadership
OL,14,Fcontest or handing power to Burnham
OL,15,Fhas gained pace among Labour figures
OL,16,Fsince he won the Makerfield by-
OL,17,Felection on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
