OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782042480
OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FThe number of Labour MPs calling for
OL,7,FStarmer to go has since topped 100 `
OL,8,Fjust under a quarter of the party's
OL,9,FMPs ` and includes some who signed a
OL,10,Fletter warning against a leadership
OL,11,Fcontest just last month.
OL,13,FLabour grandees have also spoken out,
OL,14,Fwith former home secretary Alan
OL,15,FJohnson saying Starmer should step
OL,16,Faside and Lord Falconer saying he has
OL,17,F"no authority" because it is assumed
OL,18,Fhe will be replaced.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
