OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782042480
OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister is understood to be
OL,7,Fat Chequers with his wife, Lady
OL,8,FVictoria, this weekend, and is
OL,9,Freportedly reflecting on how to
OL,10,Fproceed.
OL,12,FA senior ally told The Sun they
OL,13,Fbelieve there is "just a 25% chance he
OL,14,Ffights on now", while The Observer
OL,15,Fcited a Labour peer who said they
OL,16,Fthink Starmer sees that "stopping
OL,17,F'chaos' (as he rightly put it) is now
OL,18,Fnot possible by staying."
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@NO]xD@YOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
