CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782042480
OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FSenior Labour figures believe a "clear
OL,7,Fstatement" could come as early as
OL,8,FMonday, according to The Observer.
OL,10,FNo 10 said Starmer's position remained
OL,11,Funchanged from Friday, when he said he
OL,12,Fwill not "walk away" from Downing
OL,13,FStreet and that he plans to stand in
OL,14,Fany potential contest.
OL,16,FHe warned Labour staffers during a
OL,17,Fcall on Friday lunchtime to avoid
OL,18,F"plunging our party and our country
OL,19,Finto chaos by turning on each other
OL,20,Fand tearing apart our party and our
OL,21,Fmovement".
OL,26,@nD@aOUoD@JO]tD@JOUtD@TO]zD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
