CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782042480
OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FHe is understood to have spoken to a
OL,7,Fnumber of Cabinet ministers on Friday,
OL,8,Fsome of whom are reported to have told
OL,9,Fhim he should set out a timetable for
OL,10,Fhis departure.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FSome in Westminster believe a contest
OL,18,Fcould begin as early as next week, but
OL,19,Fallies of Burnham favour a longer wait
OL,20,Fto allow them to prepare for
OL,21,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
