PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782042480
OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FIt is understood that Burnham's camp
OL,7,Fwants Starmer to set out his plans in
OL,8,Fthe coming days, but would accept a
OL,9,Ftimetable that kept him in No 10 until
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FThe incoming Makerfield MP is expected
OL,13,Fto be in Westminster on Monday to be
OL,14,Fsworn into the Commons.
OL,16,FHe is reportedly planning to speak to
OL,17,Fthe Prime Minister afterwards and
OL,18,Fpresent him with a list of backers `
OL,19,Fwhich he is said to be seeking to get
OL,20,Fup to 200 ` in a bid to press him to
OL,21,Fstep down and set out a transition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
