PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782042480
OL,3,CStarmer under sustained pressure amid
OL,4,Creports he could step down next week
OL,6,FIn a blow to Starmer, Labour peer
OL,7,FCharlie Falconer said the Prime
OL,8,FMinister has "absolutely no authority"
OL,9,Fbecause "everybody assumes" Burnham is
OL,10,Fgoing to challenge him and win.
OL,12,FHe said he would advise Starmer not to
OL,13,Fstand in a leadership contest and
OL,14,Finstead agree a handover, preferably
OL,15,Fbefore the parliamentary recess on
OL,16,FJuly 16.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
